Overwrite Header

  • Overwrite

    • Overwrite specifies whether the server should overwrite the state of a non-null resource during a COPY or MOVE.
    • A value of “false” states that the server MUST NOT perform the COPY or MOVE operation if the state of the destination is non-null.
    • Default value is “false”
